text: AbaxitrellaGorochov AV (2002) Zoosystematica Rossica 10(2): 319. is a genus of crickets in the subfamily Podoscirtinae and tribe Podoscirtini. This genus has species recorded from southeast China and Vietnam.Orthoptera Species File (Version 5.0/5.0: retrieved 30 August 2019) == Species == Two species are currently known: *Abaxitrella hieroglyphica (Gorochov, 2002) \- type species *Abaxitrella uncinata Ma & Gorochov, 2015 == References == == External links== * Category:Ensifera genera Category:Crickets Category:Orthoptera of Indo-China
